UID:cSEIdAgilGM9M_TVcVsN3
SUMMARY:HONNE - 10 YEAR ANNIVERSARY TOUR
DTSTAMP:20260326T123259Z
DTSTART:20260623T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:A stripped back and intimate evening celebrating songs from the
	 Warm On A Cold Night and Love Me / Love Me Not albums. The Neptune is loc
	ated at 1303 Northeast 45th Street in Seattle's University District. There
	 is a ticket limit of 8 tickets per person and per credit card on this eve
	nt. Accounts found in violation of the posted ticket limit may be cancelle
	d without notice. All sales are final. No refunds or exchanges. Mobile bar
	codes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue reserves the right to cha
	nge delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must have a tic
	ket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no elevator. Stairs and
	 ramps only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. A
	rrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When purchasing 
	ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by email if assist
	ance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us
	 at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless 
	freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairments and their compani
	ons. Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator to the balcony 
	levels. A stripped back and intimate evening celebrating songs from the Wa
	rm On A Cold Night and Love Me / Love Me Not albums.\n\nhttps://www.ticket
	master.com/honne-10-year-anniversary-tour-seattle-washington-06-22-2026/ev
	ent/0F006444B30F7005\n\nFrom STG - Neptune Theatre
URL:https://www.ticketmaster.com/honne-10-year-anniversary-tour-seattle-was
	hington-06-22-2026/event/0F006444B30F7005
LOCATION:Neptune Theatre\, 1303 NE 45th Street\, Seattle\, WA
